# DLC::GET_EXTRACONTENT_CLOUD_RESULT

## Returns
* **INT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the status of the extracontent cloud transfers

This function is hard-coded to always return 0.
